From 7e97147b8ff42d41f1b7fe3a6b535eadaf6d9de5 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Work Leaf Bench <bench@example.com>
Date: Wed, 10 Jun 2026 20:45:14 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 2/3] ADD selected-agent backend commands to keep slash
 controls local

Route selected-agent chat messages like /status and /fork through AgentBackend::command_streaming so provider controls can inspect session state without sending slash-command text through the normal agent prompt and orchestrator directive path.
